      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃、ちょっと入らせてもらうな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono. I’m coming in.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2626.53069496155,
          "startTime": 3.42653069496155
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 4.683333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 4.683333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……もう。まだ何か用事ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Jeez. What do you want now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.733333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 9.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "立入禁止って言いましたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told you not to follow me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なあ琴乃、よかったら少し外に出ないか？\n本番までまだ時間はあるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Kotono. Could we step out for a moment?\nThere’s still some time before the concert.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　どこに行くんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Where do you want to go?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.166666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 19.1666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁまぁいいから\n大事なことなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just come on. Come with me.\nThis is important.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.166666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 25.7333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　この格好で行くんですか？\nえ？　えぇー？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What? You want me to go like this?\nWait. What?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3833.333333333332,
          "startTime": 32.266666666666666
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 32.016666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 32.0166666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――物販ブース",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Retail booth",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "あの……なんで物販ブースに来たんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are we doing here at the retail booth?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "イベントの運営に\n少し物販の手伝いをさせてほしいってお願いしたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I asked the operators of the event\nif you could help them with the merchandise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.91052630742391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 43.6333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　どういうことですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What? Now you’ve really lost me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、お客に見つかったら大騒ぎになる\nだから後ろの方で目立たないようにしていてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ it will cause a stampede if the fans realize you’re here.\nSo just stay at the back and don’t attract any attention.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 53.8666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 55.6666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 56.63
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "そうじゃなくて！　どうして！　今！\n物販のお手伝いをする必要があるんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m still not following! Why are we doing this now?\nWhy do I need to help sell merchandise now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 60.4333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、注文が入ったぞ\n話は後だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ here’s your first order.\nWe can talk later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.376417255401606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "ええー！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 65.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、後でちゃんと説明してもらいますから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-you’d better have a good explanation for this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 69.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*huff* *huff*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "物販のお手伝いって初めてでしたけど\nこんなに忙しいなんて知りませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was my first time helping with retail.\nI had no idea it was so hectic!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 81
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、{user}さん\nそろそろ説明してくれてもいいんじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ {user}.\nCan you explain the point of all this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 86.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今の琴乃は、恥ずかしさで周りが見えなくなってる\nだから一度他のことに集中した方がいいと思ったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were so wrapped up in being embarrassed that you couldn’t see the bigger picture.\nThat’s why I thought you needed something else to focus on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "……確かに\nあまりに忙しくて恥ずかしさも忘れてましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…True.\nI was so busy just now‚ I forgot to even be embarrassed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 100.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "だからって、もうすぐステージなのに……\nどうしてわざわざ会場の物販に？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Still‚ the concert is just about to start.\nWhy did you make me help with the merchandise?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "周りのお客さんを見てみるといい\nみんな、どんな顔をしてる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Have a look at all the customers.\nLook at their faces. How do they look?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 110.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "それは……あ、凄く楽しそう……です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They look… well‚ really happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 118.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それに、ほら\nみんなが手に持っているもの、なんだか分かるだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And look at their hands.\nWhat are they holding? What’s making them happy?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
