      "text": "そうだ、ここは月ストの物販ブース\nつまり全員が琴乃達のファンだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Correct. This is the Moon Tempest retail booth.\nWhich means these are all your fans‚ Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "みんなこれから始まるステージを楽しみにしてる\nそれに、夏らしい装いの月ストを期待してるはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They are all looking forward to the performance that’s about to start.\nAnd looking forward to the summery costumes‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 142.63333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
