      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "それは……そう、かもしれません\nいえ、そうですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure… I guess I can see that.\nNo. You’re right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、月ストのリーダーの琴乃がそんな風じゃ\nこの明るい表情を曇らせることになるんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if the leader of Moon Tempest isn’t into it‚\nwhat’s going to happen to all these happy faces?",
        "id": ""
