      "text": "リハのこと、月ストのみんなにも謝らなきゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need to apologize to everyone about the rehearsals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_02_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "心配してたからな、そうするといい。それにさ\n水着は夏の正装って言うだろ？　気にし過ぎだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good. They were all worried about you.\nAnd no need to overthink things. Swimwear is the uniform of summer!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
